H0.text: Of what type of rock is the Rock of Gibraltar made. Granite

H1.text: Of what type of rock is the Rock of Gibraltar made. Sandstone

H2.text: Of what type of rock is the Rock of Gibraltar made. Basalt

H3.text: Of what type of rock is the Rock of Gibraltar made. Limestone

A4.text: The Rock of Gibraltar is a monolithic limestone mountain

A5.text: The Main Ridge has a sharp crest with peaks over 400 metres (1,300 ft) above sea level, formed by Early Jurassic limestones and dolomites
